(195, 1, '2019-06-26 13:35:15', '2019-06-26 10:35:15', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":194} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Huawei-Enjoy-9-specs-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After Google suspended Huawei\'s future access to Android Play Store and security updates, there are serious question marks over the future of Huawei and Honor phones.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>While Google and Huawei have promised to support phones currently on the market, it\'s not clear how long they\'ll receive Android updates or access to the Google Play Store, which would severely curtail their usefulness compared to the competition.</em> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Huawei is the second biggest smartphone manufacturer in the world after Samsung, and it\'s got there by offering up some excellent devices along the way.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It\'s grown in strength significantly over the past couple of years, to the point that if you\'re looking for the best Huawei phones around, there\'s a wide range to choose from.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At the top of the range are the flagship Huawei P30 Pro and Huawei Mate 20 Pro, but our best Huawei phones list also includes great, affordable handsets such as the Huawei P Smart.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That means when it comes to picking the best Huawei phone for you, it can be tricky. With that in mind we’ve highlighted the best Huawei phones the firm currently has to offer and ranked them.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, not everyone’s budget and needs are the same, so just because something is lower in this list it doesn’t mean it will be a worse choice for you than something higher.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>And let\'s not forget, Huawei\'s most exciting phone of 2019 is yet to go on sale, with the foldable Huawei Mate X slated to land in stores in the coming months - however, with the recent issues with the Samsung Galaxy Fold it appears all foldable phones are currently on a temporary hold.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While Huawei\'s current crop of smartphones are great devices, you now need to take into consideration the long-term future of the handsets and whether or not it\'s worth the risk in investing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you\'re willing to take the risk, our list will show you at a glance their specs, highlights and main weaknesses, so you can make an informed choice as to which is the best Huawei for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The best Huawei phones of 2019: find your perfect Huawei', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '193-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-26 13:35:15', '2019-06-26 10:35:15', '', 193, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2019/06/26/193-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(196, 1, '2019-06-26 13:39:59', '2019-06-26 10:39:59', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":197} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Huawei-P30-Lite-Blue.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-197\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nThe Huawei P30 Pro is the best Huawei phone you can buy right now. It\'s the best phone we\'ve used when it comes to photography with the cameras the P30 Pro\'s real party piece, providing staggeringly good 5x and 10x zoom, and a digital 50x zoom with gets you insanely close to objects far off in the distance. Its low-light capabilities are also top-notch.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>|<strong>Release date:&nbsp;</strong>March 2019 |&nbsp;<strong>Weight:&nbsp;</strong>192g |&nbsp;<strong>Dimensions:&nbsp;</strong>158 x 73.4 x 8.4mm  |&nbsp;<strong>OS:&nbsp;</strong>Android 9 |&nbsp;<strong>Screen size:&nbsp;</strong>6.47-inch |&nbsp;<strong>CPU:&nbsp;</strong>Kirin 980 |&nbsp;<strong>RAM:&nbsp;</strong>8GB |&nbsp;<strong>Storage:&nbsp;</strong>128/256/512GB |&nbsp;<strong>Battery:&nbsp;</strong>4,200mAh |&nbsp;<strong>Rear camera:&nbsp;</strong>40MP + 20MP + 8MP + ToF |&nbsp;<strong>Front camera:&nbsp;</strong>32MP<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://amazon.com/Stunning-Display-Android-TM-Sim-Free-Smartphone/dp/B07PL5PD7V?psc=1&amp;SubscriptionId=AKIAIPHVZTVH6LZ5BFZA&amp;tag=hawk-future-20&amp;linkCode=xm2&amp;camp=2025&amp;creative=165953&amp;creativeASIN=B07PL5PD7V&amp;ascsubtag=trd-custom-tracking-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> </strong></a>Fantastic camerasEye-catching designDisplay \'only\' Full HDEMUI lacks polish</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The large 6.47-inch screen on the P30 Pro may \'only\' have a Full HD+ resolution, but it\'s bright, clear and colorful providing an excellent canvas for your apps and games.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There\'s no worry when it comes to the P30 Pro potentially running out of juice, the battery life here is excellent. We regularly got to the end of the day with 30% or more left in the tank.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The P30 Pro not only sets a new standard for Huawei, it sets a new standard for the entire mobile industry. Its cameras are quite simply astonishing, the design is eye-catching and the power plentiful. It’s a true flagship smartphone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Huawei P30 Pro', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'huawei-p30-pro', '', '', '2019-06-26 14:05:24', '2019-06-26 11:05:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=196', 0, 'post', '', 0),
